msgstr "底层内存分配由启动时选择的两个可互换层之一处理（两者都满足 ``L1ManagerProtocol``）："

#: ../../source/mp/architecture.rst:242
msgid ""
"``L1MemoryManager`` (default) -- pinned CPU DRAM, with lazy growth up to "
