msgstr "``L1MemoryManager``（默认）-- 固定的 CPU DRAM，懒惰增长至 ``--l1-size-gb``。"

#: ../../source/mp/architecture.rst:244
msgid ""
"``GDSL1MemoryManager`` -- an NVMe slab file when ``--gds-l1-path`` is "
"set. The bytes live on disk; reads/writes DMA directly between the GPU "
"staging buffer and the slab via cuFile, driven by the process-global "
"``GDSContext`` (``gpu_connector/gds_context.py``) and dispatched from "
"``gpu_ops``. The CPU tier is disabled in this mode."
msgstr "``GDSL1MemoryManager`` -- 当设置了 ``--gds-l1-path`` 时，使用 NVMe 块文件。字节存储在磁盘上；通过 cuFile 直接在 GPU 暂存缓冲区和块之间进行读/写 DMA，由进程全局的 ``GDSContext``（``gpu_connector/gds_context.py``）驱动，并从 ``gpu_ops`` 派发。在此模式下，CPU 层被禁用。"

